# Auto Collect Dataset

OpenCV for automatically collecting for labeling images for YOLO object detection training.

## Features

- 🎥 Live camera and video file capture
- 🏷️ Automatic image collection with YOLO inference

## Installation

Requires Python 3.10 or higher.

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/Fonphas/Auto_Collect_dataset.git
cd Auto_Collect_dataset

Then connect your camera or load a video file from the sidebar 
to start collecting images.
